Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), dh-python, gir1.2-ibus-1.0 (>= 1.5), gobject-introspection, intltool, libanthy-dev (>= 1:0.3-6), libgirepository1.0-dev, libglib2.0-dev, pkgconf, python3-dev, python3-gi
Description: anthy engine for IBus IBus is an Intelligent Input Bus. It is a new input framework for Linux OS. It provides full featured and user friendly input method user interface.
